{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id798c85ab-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s1891"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1891"},"text":"§ 1891.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Investment in United States seafood processing facilities","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Commerce shall work with the Small Business Administration and other Federal agencies to develop financial and other mechanisms to encourage United States investment in seafood processing facilities in the United States for fisheries that lack capacity needed to process fish harvested by United States vessels in compliance with the Magnuson-Stevens Fishery Conservation and Management Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1801"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 1801","children":[],"tail":" et seq.)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id798c85ac-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/479/tI/s106/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–479, title I, § 106(c)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2007-01-12"},"text":"Jan. 12, 2007","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/120/3593"},"text":"120 Stat. 3593","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id798c85ad-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id798c85ae-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id798c85af-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Magnuson-Stevens Fishery Conservation and Management Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/265"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–265","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-04-13"},"text":"Apr. 13, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/331"},"text":"90 Stat. 331","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to this chapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1801"},"text":"section 1801 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id798c85b0-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of the Magnuson-Stevens Fishery Conservation and Management Reauthorization Act of 2006, and not as part of the Magnuson-Stevens Fishery Conservation and Management Act which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
